{"tid":2420423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"維拉禁球員玩英超Fantasy","createTime":"2021-02-24T02:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T09:23:03.000Z","uid":72497,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d81188c4beaeff11cf77e45dffa618b6226d9687","tid":2420423,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"阿士東維拉為免軍情外洩，禁止球員玩英超Fantasy。阿士東維拉在上仗英超展開前，被爆出隊長加利殊（Jack Grealish）受傷缺陣，最終於主場以1:2不敵李斯特城。據知，軍情外洩全因多名維拉球員賽前於英超官方遊戲Fantasy Premier League中，把加利殊換走。<br />\n<br />\n領隊甸史密夫對於事件非常氣憤，聲言要調查到底。英國《每日郵報》報道，維拉決定禁止球員再玩英超Fantasy，以避免再度洩露軍情。其他英超球會也十分關注事件，雖然未有下達禁玩令，但已經告訴球員，不要再選擇自己的隊友。<br />\n<br />\n維拉現以23戰36分排英超第8位，在周六將作客列斯聯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0906bdb488350ffe41a9b48fc2c948eec3645f13","tid":2420423,"uid":318164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"冇咗佢 維拉唔識嬴"},{"pid":"708cc4bc9874e2612465a1530cc5a8994277a090","tid":2420423,"uid":234509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"不要再選擇自己的隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f37ab048a2d8451f2587f050f44ac4e56bd8870","tid":2420423,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"708cc4bc9874e2612465a1530cc5a8994277a090","tid":2420423,"uid":234509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"不要再選擇自己的隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb363ef49c3a18c7f0245e83195f307d55f414a","tid":2420423,"uid":261505,"like"